    "Generative AI uses underlying models to create new output by responding to user input and generating a response based on the learned context.",
    "Future GenAI may evolve towards multimodal models that work with different types of data.",
    "This will help to understand how large language models are used in AI and how they affect text processing and response generation in dialogue systems.",
    "Basic generative AI models have no statepreserving properties and do not improve through interaction.",
    "Their functionality is limited to generating a response to input data, without storing or assimilating information."
